Taskforce - Instruction

This is alpha "Getting Things Done" web application called Taskforce. It is heavily inspired by all the GTD apps on a mac. Like Things, OmniFocus and Hitlist.

Currently only support for Firefox 3+ / Safari 3.2+ / Google Chrome / Adobe AIR

Project structure:

	build/
		Latest build: *air, unsigned airi and the source
	page/
		Project page
	service/
		Synchronisation / Share PHP Services
	src/
		application source
	src/application
		models / controller / views
	src/library
		third party code
	src/public
		css / images
	tests/
		unit tests
	
		

Please give me all your Feedback!

